'''Willy Ndahiro''' ni Umunya[[rwanda]] wavukiye i [[bujumbura]] ,[[Burundi]] iya 1, mata 1976, wamenyekanye nka Paul muri filimi nyarwanda yakunzwe  cyane <nowiki>''Ikigeragezo cy' ubuzima", Ni umuyobozi ndetse n'</nowiki>umukinnyi wa filimi nyarwanda kuva 2006<ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/filmmaker-ndahiro-unveils-new-film-production-studio</ref>.<ref>http://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/willy-ndahiro-agiye-gusohora-filime-igaragaramo-umuhanzi-ngarambe-francois</ref>  Byatumye aba umuyobozi wa komite ishinze abakinnyi bamafilimi mu [[Rwanda]] umwanya amazeho imyaka irenga 10<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/70010/umukinnyi-wa-filime-willy-ndahiro-aramaganira-kure-ibihuha-b-70010.html</ref>. zimwe muri filimi yayoboye akanakinamo ni "Ay'urukundo"," Kanyarwanda","Anitha" na "Igisubizo cy'ubuzima".<ref>https://genesisbizz.com/Willy-Ndahiro-yagizwe-umuyobozi-mukuru-wa-Rwanda-Film-Federation-w-agateganyo</ref>

== Ubuzima bwa Willy muri make ==
Willy Ndahiro yavukiye mu [[Burundi]] muri 1976, muri 1993 we n'umuryango we batashye mu [[Rwanda]]. muri 1993 Willy yahise ajya mu gisirikare aho yabaye mu ngabo zirinda perezida kugeza 2006.<ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/147647</ref> <ref>https://www.theeastafrican.co.ke/tea/rwanda-today/lifestyle/movie-industry-needs-more-money-1311272</ref>Willy avuye mu gisirikare yasubiye kwiga arangiriza mu bumenyi bw'ikoranabuhanga, muri 2006 nibwo yatangiye inzira yo gukina filimi atangirira kuri filimi yahise ituma amenyekana "Ikigeragezo cy'ubuzima"<ref>https://kglnews.com/index.php/tag/willy-ndahiro/</ref>, muri 2010 yayoboye ndetse akina muyindi filimi yakunzwe cyane "Ay'urukundo"<ref>https://umuseke.rw/paul-wo-mu-kigeragezo-cyubuzima-azabenguka-mushiki-we-muri-film-bazanyemo.html</ref>. Willy kandi yagiye ashinga studio zitunganya amafilimi harimo iyakoze filmi nyinshi yitwa"Vision Production Ltd"<ref>https://ibyamamare.com/ndahiro-natacha-umukobwa-ufite-amafoto-akunzwe-cyane-mbuga-nkoranyambaga-kubera-uburanga-bwe-agiye-gusohora-filime-yakinanye-na-musaza-we/</ref>

